pullrequest.title: Fixed documentation, added key modifiers to KeyEvent

content.raw: ~~I did it to suppress warnings due to the initialization list in the constructor. Maybe the best thing stylistically is to put the constructor at the top and make a KeyEvent.cc with the implementation of the constructor + initialization list.~~ today I learned that the items of an initialization list need to go in the order that you declare them
content.html: I did it to suppress warnings due to the initialization list in the constructor. Maybe the best thing stylistically is to put the constructor at the top and make a KeyEvent.cc with the implementation of the constructor + initialization list. today I learned that the items of an initialization list need to go in the order that you declare them
